{
  "stem": "12882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was not my strength.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But that was not so important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My brother was similar, except with the one matter which I said before, that he just failed in many subjects because he wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was equally talented in mathematics and also performed that in a peculiar way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He did everything in his head and refused to write the way you should do it down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He only wrote the question, answer, finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he was forced by teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He was accused of cheating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Try another time and I'll show you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That's what they finally had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We played together quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And it was a great pleasure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we also performed wherever it was possible in Jewish circles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We then went to Berlin at a certain time, my brother and myself, because there was still a Jewish music school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But that came at a later date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Pretty soon, it turned out that a number of our teachers couldn't teach us anymore, I mean our musical teachers, that the Gestapo was after them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I was very lucky, because, at the age of 14, I was sent to Prague, to Czechoslovakia, which, then, was just fantastic country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "The city of Prague, very, very beautiful, still today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And very many of the Jewish people were very interested in music, especially chamber music.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I played on a Sunday from 10 o'clock in the morning until midnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Going from one group to other, being very popular.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "After all, there were not so many 15 year old one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And my general education wasn't really neglected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was enrolled at the music school, the German music school in Prague, school with a wonderful reputation.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
